wiki.content: “Changes” is the eighth release of Lauv’s studio album "~how i’m feeling~" and talks about changing yourself for the better. The song was teased on Lauv’s Twitter and Instagram on December 27, 2019. One day before its release, Lauv said: "2020 is about changing for the better so i made a song about it." In an interview with Apple Music’s Beats 1, Lauv said: "'The funny thing about the song is I actually started it about a year ago when I was honestly experiencing the worst time of my life. Like, I was just in a really low place, but the song, it’s called “Changes” and it’s about needing to change things in your life in order to be happy again and to get to a good place. It kinda took me a while, you know, this year’s been a crazy journey for me mentally and emotionally, and it took me, like, up until now to, like, fully finish it and to have the perspective.'"
